“We are talking about the successful expansion of this project, but the negotiations in Czech Republic do not seem too hopeful.
Mobilking will be launched in other countries of our region," Jana Studničková, spokesperson of the Penta Financial Group, said.
Indirectly, it has shown that the existing Czech mobile providers do not have an overcompatibility with this idea.
On the contrary, they try to do everything they can to avoid any potential competition.
The GTS Novera Group has not been hiding its interest in the launch of the virtual service provider for a while, which would therefore want to take another step to make Phoneica O2 a real competitor on the field of business customers.
