Responsible offices - a storm with service providers
The procedure of mobile operators is easy to understand, the entry of another service provider would lead to an increase in competition, a decrease in prices and thus a decrease in their profits.
Why should we facilitate the entry of such a competition?
When there is something important for service providers, they are able to work together, they also witness a huzavon around the birth of U:fon.
The biggest pressure on the ČTÚ is likely to be around the birth of the U:fon of the T-Mobile company.
