We've seen this in a few similar situations.
Unfortunately, in the text of the recently adopted Telecommunication Act, the extension of the competence of ČTÚ in the field of economic competition in the field of telecommunication failed, although many experts hoped to improve the situation.
The representatives of the UOHS need to know this well, but they probably have other interests.
It works when no one is watching
At the same time, there will be some false virtual service providers that already work in Czech mobile networks.
